''Songs of the League'' was a collection of hymns focusing on peace collected by the League of Universal Brotherhood. It was one of a number of hymnals in the 19th century used to promote social and political movements.<ref>{{cite web |last=Knoppers |first=Landon |title=New hymnals at Hymnary.org | website=Hymnary.org | date=23 July 2011 | url=https://hymnary.org/node/13692 | access-date=28 February 2018}}</ref>

